{"tid":913491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[MAGA] 感恩節 川普感謝自己「讓美國比從前更強大」","createTime":"2018-11-23T12:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T16:12:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f451a27a7576a76981890d7a1cf9ca3593f968a","tid":913491,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感恩節 川普感謝自己「讓美國比從前更強大」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E7%AF%80-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-%E8%AE%93%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%AF%94%E5%BE%9E%E5%89%8D%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7-050800991.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%2581%25A9%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1-%25E8%25AE%2593%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7-050800991.html&d=2v5n8hF6Bb1LPvXqGcPLl4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0ef8afe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E7%AF%80-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-%E8%AE%93%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%AF%94%E5%BE%9E%E5%89%8D%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7-050800991.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普在感恩節的今天說，要感謝他的家人及他擔任總統後美國出現的巨大改變，還說，正因關稅措施中國才想和美國達成協議，他已為下周「川習會」做好充分準備。<br />\n<br />\n川普今年在他集團名下的佛羅里達州海湖俱樂部（Mar-a-Lago）度感恩節假期，他上午透過電話向駐紮海外的美軍致意後，回答隨行記者問題，談到下周將赴阿根廷出席20國集團（G20）峰會，並與中國國家主席習近平會談，川普信心滿滿。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n川普稱，在感恩節的今天，他除感謝家人，還要感謝美國在他上任後出現天翻地覆的巨大改變，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「美國比從前更強大，當我上任時，你們都不相信（這會成真）」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n川普說，已為「川習會」做好充分準備，「我一生都在為此做準備」，不是現在才要坐下來研究，他對美中貿易問題的細節知之甚詳。<br />\n</span><br />\n川普還自豪，正因為他採取的關稅措施，中國現在才這麼想和美國達成協議，他也不改立場指出，現在對中國2500億美元產品的關稅稅率是10%、到明年1月1日會調升至25%。<br />\n<br />\n川普重申，關稅對美國是好事，中國過去占盡美國好處，自從他擔任總統以來，中國已損失數十兆美元，而美國經濟復甦強盛，現在是真正經濟強國。<br />\n<br />\n在與實際數字不相符下，川普說，他接手時、美國的經濟成長率是負值、為-4%、-5%或是-6%，而他上任後，美國經濟成長率已達4.2%。<br />\n<br />\n今年第2季，美國經濟成長率是4.2%，第3季預測為3.5%，而前總統歐巴馬任上的最後一年即2016年，全年四季經濟成長率都是正值，2017年1月至3月，也就是歐巴馬交棒給川普的時期，美國當季經濟成長率也有1.8%，也非負值。"},{"pid":"ecc6036f3c523101e0b662f1fbaf7fab203386d0","tid":913491,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"好想幫侵侵含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7259427abb7ae6c106597e439ea2fe51c894618b","tid":913491,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b38fd190d622f281aa6f4d9994e7e69ee3ca72b","tid":913491,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e54a41f50ebce35273f5596d2a6b3b6c6293be","tid":913491,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"得侵侵夠膽開口讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4086e06c0e7ce7bde6716911118a04f84f90cce","tid":913491,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"我要多謝我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e1173c425f06e8162255d4690b82230c114392","tid":913491,"uid":102872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"侵侵夠膽開口讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f926183fa7ee7cbc035eebd4e916a297bf3998","tid":913491,"uid":187517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好頂引"},{"pid":"e5aa220033bc5cf3c8b64836ba6a3b103498cbfc","tid":913491,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"做到嘢點解唔敢認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無侵侵個個都係左膠對支那敢怒不敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}